            <who name="Christopher Zuendorf">christopher.zuendorf</who>
            <bug_when>2012-07-18 16:47:54 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>Finally fixed Android Input Field overlay bug.

* Used no password field ( type:password), instead using webkit-text-security attribute, and type text for inputs. Password fields always had an overlay in Android webview.
* When os.name is &quot;android&quot; , iScroll does not use &quot;transform3d&quot; anymore, because this caused the overlay bug.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
